msgstr "<strong><span class=\"h1-fs\">Brugsscenarie:</span></strong>"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong><span class=\"h4-fs\">Goods</span></strong>"
msgstr "<strong><span class=\"h4-fs\">Varer</span></strong>"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong><span class=\"h4-fs\">Services</span></strong>"
msgstr "<strong><span class=\"h4-fs\">Tjenester</span></strong>"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Based on timesheets, subcontracted</strong> (Design presentation "
"&amp; revisions, this config will create a new Purchase Order to buy this "
"prestation and create a task in the dedicated project)."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Baseret på tidsregistreringer, der er udliciteret til "
"underleverandører</strong> (designpræsentation og revisioner), opretter "
"denne konfiguration en ny ordre til køb af ydelsen samt en opgave i det "
"relevante projekt."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Based on timesheets</strong> (Concept Development and 3D renderings, "
"this one will create a specific task in the existing \"3D Renderings\" "
"Project)"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Baseret på tidsregistreringer</strong> "
"(konceptudvikling og 3D-renderinger) oprettes dette som en specifik opgave i "
"det eksisterende projekt \"3D-gengivelser\""

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Based on timesheets</strong> - Field services (Delivery and "
"installation &amp; Electrical and lighting installation) will automatically "
"create a task in the Field Service App."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Baseret på tidsregistreringer</strong> – eksterne tjenester "
"(levering og installation samt el- og belysningsinstallation) – oprettes der "
"automatisk en opgave i appen til eksterne tjenester."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Basics:</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Det grundlæggende:</strong>"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Components </strong>that will serve to create manufactured products."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Komponenter,</strong> der anvendes til fremstilling af færdige "
"produkter."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Consumable goods:</strong> These will not be tracked (Such as bolts, "
"finish painting, and sandpaper)."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Forbrugsvarer:</strong> Disse spores ikke "
"(f.eks. skruer, maling og sandpapir)."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Jane Design</strong>: She is your subcontractor for Design "
"presentations and revisions."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Jane Design</strong>: Hun fungerer som underleverandør for "
"designpræsentationer og -revisioner."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Manufactured Goods </strong>will be manufactured based on a Bill of "
"Material."
msgstr "<strong>Færdige varer </strong>fremstilles på baggrund af styklisten."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>My Chairs Vendor</strong>: Will provide you Conference chairs to "
"complete your order."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Min stoleleverandør</strong>: Leverer konferencestole til dig som "
"led i færdiggørelsen af din ordre."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>My Metal Vendor</strong>: Will provide the Conference Table Metal "
"Legs you need to manufacture the conference table."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Min metalleverandør</strong>: Leverer metalbenene til "
"konferencebordet, som er nødvendige for fremstillingen af bordet."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>My Rug Vendor</strong>: Will provide you the custom area rug in "
"sufficient square meters."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Min tæppehandler</strong>: Leverer det skræddersyede tæppe i den "
"nødvendige størrelse."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>My Wood Vendor</strong>: Will send you the Oak Wood Panels you need "
"to create the tables."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Min træleverandør</strong>: Leverer de nødvendige egetræsplader til "
"produktionen af bordene."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Prepaid services, fixed price</strong> (Initial design consultation "
"&amp; Final Inspection. Note that the first one will also create a new "
"project for each confirmed order to ensure Project follow-up)."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Forudbetalte tjenester til fast pris</strong> "
"(første designkonsultation og endelig godkendelse). Bemærk, at der ved den "
"første konsultation også oprettes et nyt projekt for hver bekræftet ordre, "
"så opfølgning på projektet sikres."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Purchased Goods</strong> that will be purchased and sold to your "
"customers."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Købte varer,</strong> der anskaffes med henblik på videresalg til "
"kunder."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"A Quality Check Point has been set for each product. It requires your worker "
"or the Quality Team to take a picture of any manufactured item. Use any "
"image to pass the check for this demo."
msgstr ""
"Der er fastsat et kvalitetskontrolpunkt for hvert produkt. Din medarbejder "
"eller kvalitetsteam skal tage et foto af hvert fremstillet produkt. I denne "
"demo kan du bruge et vilkårligt billede for at bestå testen."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model:product.template,name:custom_furniture.product_product_7_product_template
msgid "Accent chairs"
msgstr "Accentstole"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"All these components will give you an accurate overview on the project "
"profitability."
msgstr ""
"Alle disse komponenter giver dig et klart overblik over projektets "
"rentabilitet."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Analytic Items ➡️ Track any cost using Analytic Items from the Accounting App"
msgstr ""
"Koststedsbogføringer ➡️ Hold styr på alle omkostninger med "
"koststedsbogføringer fra regnskabsappen"

