#: model:planning.role,name:custom_furniture.planning_role_2
msgid "Architect"
msgstr "Arkitekt"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid "Basics:"
msgstr "Det grundlæggende:"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Before generating an intermediary invoice in the\n"
"                <strong>\n"
"                        <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Invoicing</font>\n"
"                </strong>\n"
"                app, freeze the project status in the\n"
"                <strong>\n"
"                        <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Project</font>\n"
"                </strong>\n"
"                app to get an overview of the progress in terms of:"
msgstr ""
"Inden du genererer en mellemfaktura i\n"
"                <strong>\n"
"                        <font class=\"text-o-color-1\""
">Faktureringsappen,</font>\n"
"                </strong>\n"
"                skal du fryse projektstatus i\n"
"                <strong>\n"
"                        <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Projektappen</font>\n"
"                </strong>\n"
"                for at få et overblik over fremskridtene med hensyn til:"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid "Bills of Materials"
msgstr "Styklister"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model:product.attribute.value,name:custom_furniture.product_attribute_value_1
msgid "Black"
msgstr "Sort"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model:product.attribute.value,name:custom_furniture.product_attribute_value_3
msgid "Blue"
msgstr "Blå"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By default, there is a filter on \"Sales\" products; remove it from the "
"search bar to see all products available."
msgstr ""
"Som standard er filteret for salgsprodukter aktiveret. Fjern det i "
"søgefeltet for at se alle tilgængelige produkter."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By uploading this module's demo data, your database has been filled with a "
"complete flow from the opportunity to delivery and some demo data to execute "
"the flows described hereunder."
msgstr ""
"Ved at uploade demodataene for dette modul blev din database fyldt med en "
"komplet proces fra salgsmulighed til levering samt nogle demo-data, så du "
"uden problemer kan udføre de følgende processer."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model:sale.order.template.line,name:custom_furniture.sale_order_template_line_1
msgid "Concept & Creation"
msgstr "Koncept og udarbejdelse"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model:product.template,name:custom_furniture.product_product_3_product_template
msgid "Concept development and 3D renderings"
msgstr "Konceptudvikling og 3D-gengivelser"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model:product.template,name:custom_furniture.product_template_19
msgid "Conference Table Metal Legs"
msgstr "Metallben til konferencebord"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model:product.template,name:custom_furniture.product_product_9_product_template
msgid "Conference chairs"
msgstr "Konferencestole"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Confirm the quotation. Your top bar shows that it creates different tasks in "
"different projects, an upcoming delivery, a purchase, and various hours to "
"plan. These are all automated actions based on your product configuration.\n"
"                These will be detailed in the following topics."
msgstr ""
"Bekræft tilbuddet. Din øverste menulinje viser, at der er oprettet "
"forskellige opgaver i forskellige projekter, en forestående levering, et køb "
"og forskellige timer, der skal planlægges. Dette er alle automatiserede "
"handlinger, der er baseret på din produktkonfiguration.\n"
"                Disse beskrives detaljeret i de følgende emner."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create a down payment from the sales order as the first invoicing step. This "
"will generate the first invoice in the\n"
"                <strong>\n"
"                        <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Invoicing</font>\n"
"                </strong>\n"
"                app. Then, schedule one or several \"Invoicing Schedule\" "
"activities on the sales order so you never forget to send an intermediary "
"invoice to sustain your cash flow."
msgstr ""
"Opret en forskudsbetaling fra salgsordren som det første faktureringstrin. "
"Dette genererer den første faktura i\n"
"                <strong>\n"
"                        <font class=\"text-o-color-1\""
">Faktureringsappen.</font>\n"
"                </strong>\n"
"                Planlæg derefter en eller flere \"Faktureringsplan\"-"
"aktiviteter på salgsordren, så du aldrig glemmer at sende en mellemfaktura "
"og dermed opretholder din pengestrøm."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create a stunning <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">website</font></"
"strong> and start receiving orders directly in Odoo. Go live with your "
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">E-shop</font></strong> in a few\n"
"                        minutes."
msgstr ""
"Lav en flot <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">hjemmeside,</font></"
"strong> start med at modtage ordrer direkte i Odoo. Gå live med din "
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">netbutik</font></strong> på få\n"
"                        minutter."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create an opportunity each time you face a potential customer, receive a "
"phone call, etc."
msgstr ""
"Opret en salgsmulighed, hver gang du møder en potentiel kunde, modtager et "
"opkald eller lignende."

