"Brug <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Hjemmesideappen</font></strong> "
"til at oprette en kontaktformular, der automatisk sender alle forespørgsler "
"videre til <strong> <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">CRM</font></strong>."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the Planning in the Field Service <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">​"
"</font> </strong> app to organize the work of your employees. Define which "
"project and when they have to work. Easily manage shift conflicts, workload, "
"and\n"
"                replacements in case of leave."
msgstr ""
"Brug planlægningsfunktionen i appen Udkørende Service <strong><font class="
"\"text-o-color-1\">​</font> </strong> til at organisere dine medarbejderes "
"arbejde. Bestem, hvilket projekt de skal arbejde på, og hvornår. Håndtér "
"nemt skifteholdsændringer, arbejdsbyrde og\n"
"                afløsninger i tilfælde af fravær."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:web_tour.tour,rainbow_man_message:custom_furniture.knowledge_tour
msgid "Welcome! Happy exploring."
msgstr "Velkommen! God fornøjelse med at gå på opdagelse."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When you are done with your production, you can finally deliver the complete "
"order to your customer. To do so, navigate to the Field Service Apps. From "
"the Installation task, you can see 31 Products that require pick-up. Click\n"
"                on the smart button and validate this picking."
msgstr ""
"Når produktionen er afsluttet, leveres ordren til kunden. Åbn appen til "
"eksternt arbejde, gå til opgaven \"Installation\", gennemse de 31 produkter, "
"der skal plukkes. Klik\n"
"                på den intelligente knap, og bekræft plukningen."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr ""
"Vil du gerne tale med os om dit Odoo-setup eller drøfte nogle spørgsmål mere "
"detaljeret?"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Du kan tilgå alle installerede apps i din Odoo-database direkte fra "
"hoveddashboardet."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can adapt your overview for each project by selecting the small "
"\"Sliders\" icon at the top right of your screen. It will allow you to add a "
"bunch of practical views to get the complete overview of your project, "
"including* :"
msgstr ""
"Du kan tilpasse oversigten for hvert projekt ved at klikke på det lille "
"\"skyder\"-ikon øverst til højre på skærmen. Her kan du tilføje forskellige "
"visninger, så du får et komplet overblik over projektet, herunder*:"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can add other views with specific filters and ease your project follow-"
"up."
msgstr ""
"Du kan tilføje flere visninger med specifikke filtre, så det bliver lettere "
"at følge med i dit projekt."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid "You can also find 4 different kinds of goods:"
msgstr "Der findes også fire forskellige typer varer:"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can see a new Manufacture order has been posted by navigating into "
"Operations &gt; Manufacture Orders."
msgstr ""
"Gå til \"Processer\" &gt; \"Produktionsordrer\" for at se den nyligt "
"oprettede produktionsordre."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You completed that demo use case! There are millions of other ways to adapt "
"your Odoo setup to fit your business needs."
msgstr ""
"Du har nu gennemført demoens brugsscenarie. Odoo kan tilpasses på utallige "
"måder, så løsningen matcher netop din virksomheds behov."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it if you like. Go to Apps "
"&gt; Industries &gt; Upgrade your Custom Furniture Production package and "
"check the related box."
msgstr ""
"Hvis demodata ikke er importeret, kan du stadig gøre det. Gå til Apps &gt; "
"Brancher &gt; Opdatér pakken til produktion af specialfremstillede møbler, "
"og markér det relevante felt."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You just installed the Odoo package for Custom Furniture Production "
"companies. By doing so, we have installed many necessary apps to run your "
"company efficiently."
msgstr ""
"Du har netop installeret Odoo-pakken til produktion af skræddersyede møbler. "
"Samtidig er mange nødvendige apps blevet installeret, så din virksomhed kan "
"drives effektivt."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You should be able to execute the following flows to have an overview of "
"various actions you can quickly execute with this package using Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Med denne pakke i Odoo kan du gennemføre følgende flows for hurtigt at få "
"overblik over de forskellige processer."

